Trade/Device Name(s): Rightest Blood Glucose Monitoring System GM700
Rightest Blood Glucose Monitoring System GM650
GE300 Talking Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Bionime Corporation Rightest GM700/GM650 and GE200/GE300 blood glucose monitoring systems using dehydrogenase electrochemical biosensor technology
Indications for Use Summary: Quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from fingertips, forearm, or palm for self-testing by individuals with diabetes at home as an aid to monitor the effectiveness of diabetes control; not for diagnosis, screening, or neonatal use.
